sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as App API
    participant River as River Queue (DB)
    participant Worker as Background Worker
    participant Tool as Tool Layer
    participant External as CRM / External API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    
    User->>App: "Generate a sales report and email it to the client."
    App->>River: Insert Job (GenerateReport)
    App-->>User: "I'm working on that now..."
    
    River->>Worker: Dequeue & Claim Job (Short Transaction)
    Worker->>Worker: Analyze Request, Extract Parameters
    Worker->>Tool: Execute 'DraftReport' & 'SendEmail' (Write Tool)
    Tool->>Tool: Check Idempotency Key
    Tool->>External: POST /send-email (Outside DB Transaction)
    External-->>Tool: 200 OK
    Tool->>DB: Insert AuditLog Record
    Worker->>River: Mark Job Complete (Short Transaction)
    
    Worker->>App: Push Notification (Callback)
    App-->>User: "The report has been sent!"
